    section#try.hidden
      div#error
      textarea#source:"asdf"
        @spellcheck="false"
      pre
        code#output:"asdf"

    section#content
      h1:"liten"
      p
        :"Need better structure for your HTML? You've come to the right place!"

      p
        :"liten is a small (liten in Swedish) but powerful HTML pre-processor 
        running in node.js. Packed with features such as imports, variables 
        and mixins!"

      div.code-label:"liten:"
      pre
        code.coffeescript
          :'
html
  body
    h1: "Hello World!"
    a: "Go to liten on GitHub"
      @href = "https://github.com/carlcalderon/liten"
          '
      div.code-label:"output:"
      pre
        code.html
          :'
&lt;html&gt;
  &lt;body&gt;
    &lt;h1&gt;Hello World!&lt;/h1&gt;
    &lt;a href="https://github.com/carlcalderon/liten"&gt;Go to liten on GitHub&lt;/a&gt;
  &lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;
          '
      section#introduction
        h2:"Introduction"
        p
          :"liten aims to be simple and understandable. You define 
          classes with <code>.</code>, ID's with <code>#</code> and attributes 
          width <code>@</code>. It's that simple!"

        h3:"Tags"
        p
          :"For every line you type, the first item on that line would probably
          be a Tag."

        div.code-label:"liten:"
        pre
          code.coffeescript
            :'
html
  body
    header
      nav
        ul
          li
    footer
            '
        div.code-label:"output:"
        pre
          code.html
            :'
&lt;html&gt;
  &lt;body&gt;
    &lt;header&gt;
      &lt;nav&gt;
        &lt;ul&gt;
          &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ul&gt;
      &lt;/nav&gt;
    &lt;/header&gt;
    &lt;footer&gt;&lt;/footer&gt;
  &lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;
            '

        h3:"Attributes, content, ID's and classes"
        p
          :"What would HTML be without the properties? You know, classes, widths
          and heights, data and id's. liten can handle all that too you know. If
          it wasn't easy it wouldn't be liten."

        div.code-label:"liten:"
        pre
          code.coffeescript
            :'
html
  body
    header
      nav#main-navigation
        ul
          li \ a @href = "#home" :"Home"
          li \ a @href = "#portfolio" :"Portfolio"
    footer.fix-at-bottom
            '
        div.code-label:"output:"
        pre
          code.html
            :'
&lt;html&gt;
  &lt;body&gt;
    &lt;header&gt;
      &lt;nav id="main-navigation"&gt;
        &lt;ul&gt;
          &lt;li&gt;
            &lt;a href="#home"&gt;Home&lt;/a&gt;
          &lt;/li&gt;
          &lt;li&gt;
            &lt;a href="#portfolio"&gt;Portfolio&lt;/a&gt;
          &lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ul&gt;
      &lt;/nav&gt;
    &lt;/header&gt;
    &lt;footer class="fix-at-bottom"&gt;&lt;/footer&gt;
  &lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;
            '
        h3:"- Sold! Now show me the awesome stuff."
        p
          :"- Alrighty."
        p
          :"Guess you want <strong>imports</strong>, <strong>mixins</strong> and
          <strong>variables</strong> too, right? We've got 'em all!"

        div.code-label:"liten:"
        pre
          code.coffeescript
            :'
@import mySettings
@import thatOtherLibrary

&dollar;highfive = "_o/\o_"

@mixin makeThisLookCool(&dollar;text)
  strong.blink.huge.unicorn
    :&dollar;text

+makeThisLookCool("Hello")
+makeThisLookCool("World")

div:"&dollar;highfive, alright!"
            '
        
        div.code-label:"output:"
        pre
          code.html
            :'
&lt;strong class="blink huge unicorn"&gt;Hello&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;strong class="blink huge unicorn"&gt;World&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;div&gt;_o/\o_, alright!&lt;/div&gt;
            '